{"tid":831253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解而家啲學生傾計會用普通話","createTime":"2018-09-21T18:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T19:27:10.000Z","uid":107183,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"13eb49db03c44f79a859e3434d6f707b79b59e84","tid":831253,"uid":107183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:53:13.000Z","msg":"理性討論，唔係想撩交嗌<br />\n我真係諗唔明<br />\n香港人母語係廣東話<br />\n周遭環境都係用廣東話<br />\n你話上堂要用我可以理解<br />\n點解出到街同班同學傾計都要用普通話？<br />\n<br />\n係咩理由驅使？<br />\n係因為習慣？講咗都意識唔到？<br />\n係為咗令母語係普通話嘅同學容易啲理解？<br />\n<br />\n身邊無相關年齡層嘅人<br />\n所以真係唔明，亦唔想亂估<br />\n如果有人知原因或者遇過呢啲情況<br />\n可唔可以嘗試解釋下呢種現象？<br />\n<br />\n見住啲學生放咗學行街，著住校服<br />\n然後三五成群咁講普通話傾計<br />\n我其實覺得好恐怖<br />\n唔知過幾年會唔會連我自己都習慣埋呢種現象 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7735b365a9b63acd5218dd500443eecc86dbdc","tid":831253,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:54:12.000Z","msg":"埋堆"},{"pid":"69b7e1ba7d4e6ec4b2d49e6e8ea79b1f55ea332c","tid":831253,"uid":211537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:57:51.000Z","msg":"你又知人地母語係廣東話"},{"pid":"836dbcaa64a5942f7d74e656c639550e0712617f","tid":831253,"uid":200872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:58:55.000Z","msg":"每日150<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> we trust"},{"pid":"d63e97d4126d6028d7e6960067b710752acc1571","tid":831253,"uid":14019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:59:59.000Z","msg":"當你身邊啲同學全部都係鮮腥港人，全部講普通話又唔肯講粵語，你會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上一代啲新移民至少肯學廣東話，融入香港生活，但呢一代係反客為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c88d2f7b6fc676058d3f4447db6688c0560f44","tid":831253,"uid":107183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f7735b365a9b63acd5218dd500443eecc86dbdc","tid":831253,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime